rComments: Prof O Neill's lectures are organized but can be hard to follow sometimes. Shows lots of knowledge of dev psych, talks about interesting case studies, but some lectures can be dull sometimes. Midterm averages were low, but the usual for UofT. Prepare to work hard and ask questions, because some sections can be unclear sometimes. Memorize diagrams!
